{"tid":2419509,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★滙控倫敦股價受壓 比本港收市價低近2%","createTime":"2021-02-23T10:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T10:42:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc4c502e0433340c6d5b7f57e22865c0f1966c2","tid":2419509,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"滙控倫敦股價受壓，一度跌2.5%，低見420.9便士，折合約45.93港元，比本港今日收市價46.7元低1.6%。 滙控去年列帳稅前盈利87.77億美元，按年跌34%，但仍好過市場預期，並一如預期恢復派息，每股普通股派息15美仙，不設以股代息。 集團表示，短期內不會考慮回購，今年不會按季度派息，8月公布中期業績時會考慮是否派發一次股息。另外，計劃明年開始，逐步將目標派息比例定於列帳基準每股普通股盈利的40%至55%。 滙控表示，著重亞洲市場及財富管理業務，並計劃加大科技投資。集團目標至2022年底削減3.5萬名人手，減至20萬人的目標不變，目前已減少約1.1萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93-%E6%AF%94%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E4%BD%8E%E8%BF%912-100015322.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A3%2593-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25BF%25912-100015322.html&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv354O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=e06a23a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93-%E6%AF%94%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E4%BD%8E%E8%BF%912-100015322.html</a>"},{"pid":"bdbe45c3ad288adac1597a3d21e1e2dec829e57e","tid":2419509,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" 